<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id773f889e-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s407m–4"><num value="407m–4">§ 407m–4.</num><heading> Erection of replica of Graff House; maintenance</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Secretary is further authorized to erect on the site aforesaid, with donated funds, a replica of the Graff House and to furnish and maintain the same.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id773f889f-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5">(<ref href="/us/pl/88/477/s2">Pub. L. 88–477, § 2</ref>, <date date="1964-08-21">Aug. 21, 1964</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/78/587">78 Stat. 587</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
<notes type="uscNote" id="id773f88a0-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5">
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="editorialNotes" id="id773f88a1-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"><heading class="centered"><b>Editorial Notes</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I76" topic="codification" id="id773f88a2-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Codification</heading>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Section was not enacted as a part of <ref href="/us/act/1948-06-28/ch687">act June 28, 1948, ch. 687</ref>, <ref href="/us/stat/62/1061">62 Stat. 1061</ref>, as amended, which comprises this subchapter.</p>
</note>
</notes>
